Source: jabberd2
Section: net
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Harald Braumann <harry@unheit.net>
Homepage: http://jabberd2.xiaoka.com/
Build-Depends: debhelper, autotools-dev, libexpat1-dev, libidn11-dev, libgsasl7-dev (>= 0.2.14), libssl-dev, libmysqlclient15-dev, libpq-dev, libsqlite3-dev, libdb4.2-dev, libldap2-dev, libpam0g-dev, libntlm0-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: jabberd2-common
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: Next generation Jabber/XMPP server -- common files
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains common files for the jabberd2 server.

Package: jabberd2-authreg-anon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: jabberd2-authreg
Description: Jabber/XMPP server -- anonymous authentication package
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains the authentication/registration package
 for anonymous access.

