Package: jabberd2-router
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jabberd2-common
Description: Jabber/XMPP server -- route component
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains the router component, which is used by all
 the other components to communicate to each other.

Package: jabberd2-s2s
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jabberd2-common
Description: Jabber/XMPP server -- s2s component
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains the s2s (server to server) component, which 
 handles the communication with other Jabber servers.

Package: jabberd2-c2s
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jabberd2-common, jabberd2-authreg-pam | jabberd2-authreg
Description: Jabber/XMPP server -- c2s component
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains the c2s (client to server) component, which
 handles connections from clients.

Package: jabberd2-sm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, jabberd2-common, jabberd2-storage-db | jabberd2-storage
Description: Jabber/XMPP server -- sm component
 jabberd 2.x series is the next generation of the Jabber/XMPP server.
 It has been rewritten from the ground up to be scalable, 
 architecturally sound and to support the latest protocol extensions 
 coming out of the XSF.
 .
 This package contains the sm (session manager) component, which
 handles the buld of the IM functionality, like message passing,
 presence, roster, etc.
